        "subject": "LU-20134 tests: Wait for background processes in lockorder.sh",
        "message": "LU-20134 tests: Wait for background processes in lockorder.sh\n\nlockorder.sh kills createmany and statmany but does not wait for\nthem to exit before rm -rf. It is possible that the createmany\nis still creating new files when lockdir is being removed, causing\n\"cannot remove '/mnt/lustre/lockdir': Directory not empty\".\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=sanityn env=ONLY=12\nSigned-off-by: Xiao Yang <xyang@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I0e88c09ae75a2fbb365d03c580feea12559fdd54\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
